a%20short%20scene%20of%20the%20Artist%20dancing%20in%20the%20rain%20with%20a%20hummingbird.%20This%20references%20the%20musical%20movie%20%26quot%3BSingin'%20in%20the%20Rain%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20dancer%20Gene%20Kelly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20first%20part%20of%20the%20movie%20hints%20that%20the%20Artist%20is%20the%20rose%2C%20but%20she's%20actually%20the%20hummingbird.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jennifer%20Lopez%20in%20%26quot%3BThis%20Is%20Me...%20Now%3A%20A%20Love%20Story.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cfad87a610a9069d5a0445%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJennifer%20Lopez%20in%20%26quot%3BThis%20Is%20Me...%20Now%3A%20A%20Love%20Story.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EPrime%20Video%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20red%20flower%20and%20the%20hummingbird%20from%20the%20Ta%C3%ADno%20legend%20appear%20throughout%20the%20film.%20There%20are%20even%20moments%20where%20a%20hummingbird%20hovers%20around%20the%20Artist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20of%20the%20movie%2C%20it%20is%20implied%20that%20the%20Artist%20is%20a%20rose%20waiting%20to%20be%20found%20by%20her%20lover.%20In%20the%20first%20wedding%20scene%2C%20she%20wears%20a%20red%20rose%20on%20her%20wedding%20dress.%20When%20she%20visits%20The%20Bronx%20in%20her%20dreams%2C%20she%20sees%20a%20vase%20of%20red%20flowers%20kept%20behind%20a%20shop%20window%2C%20which%20she%20thinks%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20her%20future%20romance.%20Later%20in%20the%20same%20dream%2C%20when%20the%20Artist%20is%20visited%20by%20her%20younger%20self%2C%20the%20young%20self%20eventually%20disappears%20by%20turning%20into%20red%20flower%20petals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20movie%2C%20it%20becomes%20clear%20that%20the%20Artist%20is%20not%20the%20flower%2C%20but%20the%20hummingbird.%20In%20the%20final%20scene%2C%20she%20sports%20a%20visible%20hummingbird%20tattoo%20at%20Mike's%20wedding.%20In%20addition%2C%20when%20she%20meets%20the%20mystery%20man%20at%20the%20end%2C%20%3Cem%3Ehe%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20wearing%20a%20rose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20Is%20Me...%20Now%3A%20A%20Love%20Story%2C%26quot%3B%20then%2C%20isn't%20a%20movie%20about%20a%20woman%20waiting%20for%20a%20man.%20It%20is%20about%20a%20woman%20searching%20for%20love%20and%20finding%20it%20in%20herself%20first%2C%20before%20finding%20The%20One.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthis-is-me-now-a-love-story-easter-eggs-details-you-missed-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708172642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cfb0f7a610a9069d5a080d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthis-is-me-now-a-love-story-easter-eggs-details-you-missed-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jennifer%20Lopez's%20new%20movie%20on%20Prime%20Video%20is%20loosely%20based%20on%20her%20own%20life%20and%20features%20songs%20from%20her%20new%20album%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20Is%20Me...%20Now.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aadekaiyero%40insider.com%20(Ayomikun%20Adekaiyero%2COlivia%20Singh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthis-is-me-now-a-love-story-easter-eggs-details-you-missed-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Isro%20successfully%20places%20weather%20satellite%20Insat-3DS%20into%20orbit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708172635000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107780418%2Cimgsize-1342743.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fisros-gslv-f14insat-3ds-mission-successful-satellite-to-enhance-weather-forecast%2Farticleshow%2F107780433.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22U%20TEJONMAYAM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Election%20Commission's%20FAQs%20on%20EVM-VVPATs%20Don't%20Clear%20Cloud%20of%20Suspicion%20Over%20Electoral%20Process%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10211621%2FEffect-2024-02-10T202212.238.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20refused%20to%20grant%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%20an%20urgent%20hearing%20of%20its%202021%20petition%20about%20a%20host%20of%20matters%20relating%20to%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20One%20of%20the%20major%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20petitioner%20as%20the%20basis%20for%20seeking%20an%20urgent%20hearing%20is%20the%20suitability%20of%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20and%20voter%20verifiable%20paper%20audit%20trail%20(VVPAT)%20units%20for%20ascertaining%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20mandate.%20The%20Bench%20seemed%20visibly%20exasperated%20by%20what%20it%20called%20%E2%80%93%20the%20repeated%20filing%20of%20petitions%20which%20cast%20aspersions%20on%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20layperson%2C%20these%20remarks%20hint%20at%20the%20Bench%E2%80%99s%20faith%20in%20the%20infallibility%20of%20the%20machine-based%20voting%20system%20based%20on%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20(ECI)%20claims%20as%20the%20respondent%20to%20the%20petition.%20A%20few%20weeks%20before%20this%20hearing%20took%20place%2C%20the%20ECI%20had%20released%20a%20revised%20set%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Fevm-faq-new%5C%22%3E100%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Fevm-faq-new%5C%22%3E%20FAQs%3C%2Fa%3E%20(frequently%20asked%20questions)%20with%20the%20objective%20of%20clarifying%20all%20doubts%20about%20these%20electoral%20machines.%20Several%20experts%20have%20commented%20about%20these%20FAQs%20in%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felection-commissions-faqs-on-evms-dont-really-address-major-design-deficiencies%5C%22%3Ecolumns%3C%2Fa%3E%20already.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20upon%20a%20time%2C%20I%20would%20also%20press%20the%20EVM%20button%20(both%20before%20and%20after%20the%20introduction%20of%20VVPATs)%20with%20full%20confidence%20in%20the%20reliability%20and%20infallibility%20of%20the%20electronic%20voting%20system.%20Having%20witnessed%20a%20demonstration%20of%20the%20electronic%20voting%20system%20at%20Nirvachan%20Sadan%2C%20several%20years%20ago%2C%20where%20a%20senior%20officer%20showed%20how%20these%20machines%20work%20and%20what%20fool-proof%20administrative%20measures%20are%20put%20in%20place%20to%20ensure%20their%20safe%20custody%20and%20transport%2C%20before%2C%20during%2C%20and%20after%20parliamentary%20and%20assembly%20elections%2C%20there%20was%20reason%20to%20entertain%20any%20kind%20of%20doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20this%20is%20what%20the%20ECI%20proudly%20claims%20in%20its%20FAQ%202%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6no%20technical%20knowledge%20is%20required%20for%20casting%20a%20vote%20on%20the%20EVM%20and%20ordinary%20citizens%20can%20easily%20cast%20their%20votes%20on%20ECI%20EVMs%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20public%20education%20campaigns%20the%20ECI%20launches%20prior%20to%20every%20general%20or%20bye-election%20are%20limited%20to%20such%20demonstrations%20only.%20One%20such%20awareness%20drive%20is%20going%20on%20across%20the%20country%20even%20as%20I%20write%20this%20piece.%20We%20are%20expected%20to%20take%20the%20reliability%20of%20EVMs%20as%20an%20article%20of%20faith%20based%20on%20what%20the%20ECI%20shows%20and%20tells%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668180%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20building%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40PIB_INDIA.%20November%205%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20also%20a%20tricky%20thing%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98voters%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20know%E2%80%99%20which%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20discovered%20more%20than%2022%20years%20ago.%20The%20court%20recognised%20every%20voter%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20receive%20information%20about%20the%20educational%20qualifications%2C%20financial%20background%2C%20and%20criminal%20antecedents%2C%20if%20any%2C%20of%20every%20electoral%20candidate%2C%20so%20that%20they%20choose%20wisely%20between%20those%20with%20a%20clean%20and%20tainted%20background.%20Incidentally%2C%20it%20was%20ADR%20that%20had%20moved%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20not%20once%2C%20but%20twice%2C%20to%20have%20this%20right%20read%20into%20Article%2019%20(1)(a)%20of%20the%20constitution%20which%20guarantees%20free%20speech%20and%20expression%20to%20every%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20it%20then%20be%20said%20that%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20know%20is%20limited%20to%20accessing%20details%20about%20the%20public%20character%20of%20electoral%20candidates%20and%20nothing%20more%20relating%20to%20the%20electoral%20process%3F%20Does%20it%20not%20extend%20to%20seeking%20adequate%20knowledge%20about%20the%20current%20voting%20system%20which%20is%20facilitated%20through%20machines%2C%20unlike%20the%20paper-based%20system%20that%20was%20the%20primary%20balloting%20method%20until%20a%20decade%20ago%3F%20Prior%20to%20pressing%20the%20EVM%20button%20of%20choice%2C%20voters%20play%20another%20equally%20important%20role.%20As%20taxpayers%2C%20we%20provide%20the%20funds%20with%20which%20the%20ECI%20buys%20these%20machines.%20So%2C%20these%20machines%20are%20made%20for%20our%20use%20and%20we%20have%20the%20right%20to%20ask%20questions%20to%20resolve%20every%20one%20of%20our%20doubts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20ask%20questions%20about%20these%20machines%20above%20and%20beyond%20what%20the%20ECI%20already%20tells%20us%3F%20A%20comparison%20between%20paper-based%20and%20electronic%20voting%20systems%20will%20reveal%20the%20foundation%20on%20which%20these%20doubts%20start%20to%20crop%20up.%20In%20a%20paper-based%20system%2C%20the%20ECI%20through%20its%20appointed%20functionaries%20gets%20a%20ballot%20paper%20printed%20with%20the%20names%20of%20all%20independent%20and%20political%20party-ticketed%20candidates%20along%20with%20their%20allotted%20symbols.%20All%20that%20the%20registered%20voter%20%E2%80%93%20literate%20and%20unlettered%2C%20both%20%E2%80%93%20had%20to%20do%20was%20simply%20take%20a%20ballot%20paper%20and%20a%20rubber%20stamp%20from%20the%20Presiding%20Officer%2C%20go%20to%20the%20polling%20booth%2C%20stamp%20the%20cross%20mark%20against%20the%20preferred%20candidate%20and%20drop%20it%20in%20the%20ballot%20box%20oneself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ballot%20paper%20was%20even%20pre-folded%20while%20being%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20voter.%20The%20voter%20was%20able%20to%20see%20every%20step%20of%20this%20action%20sequence%20with%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20eyes%20or%20with%20the%20help%20of%20an%20assistant%20if%20the%20person%20was%20blind.%20On%20counting%20day%2C%20the%20counting%20agents%20of%20candidates%20could%20see%20every%20ballot%20paper%20%E2%80%93%20both%20valid%20and%20invalid%20%E2%80%93%20while%20it%20was%20being%20counted%20before%20the%20results%20were%20announced.%20Nothing%20was%20hidden%20from%20the%20naked%20eye%20(with%20or%20without%20prescription%20glasses)%20as%20everything%20except%20the%20recording%20of%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20choice%20on%20the%20ballot%20was%20clearly%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20contrast%20this%20with%20the%20electronic%20voting%20system.%20There%20is%20a%20Ballot%20Unit%20(BU)%20with%20the%20names%20of%20candidates%20displayed%20on%20a%20printed%20label%20affixed%20on%20top%20of%20it.%20The%20voter%20presses%20the%20button%20next%20to%20the%20name%20and%20symbol%20of%20the%20preferred%20candidate%20in%20the%20polling%20booth%20and%20after%20it%20beeps%20something%20happens%20(we%20will%20explain%20below%20why%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20say%20anything%20more%20specific%20than%20this).%20Then%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20gets%20into%20action%20and%20prints%20out%20a%20slip%20which%20is%20visible%20to%20the%20voter%20for%20seven%20seconds%20through%20an%20illuminated%20window.%20This%20slip%20contains%20the%20name%2C%20serial%20number%20and%20symbol%20of%20the%20candidate%20in%20favour%20of%20whom%20the%20voter%20pressed%20the%20button.%20Then%20it%20automatically%20gets%20cut%20and%20falls%20down%20into%20the%20VVPAT%E2%80%99s%20drop%20box%20and%20the%20light%20is%20turned%20off.%20Next%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98loud%20beep%20is%20heard%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20according%20to%20the%20ECI%2C%20completes%20the%20action%20sequence%20of%20voting%20from%20casting%20to%20its%20registration%20in%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo.%20Only%20one%20stage%20of%20this%20process%20is%20visible%20to%20the%20voter%2C%20namely%2C%20the%20printed%20VVPAT%20slip%2C%20to%20satisfy%20oneself%20that%20the%20vote%20has%20been%20printed%20as%20per%20one%E2%80%99s%20choice.%20What%20gets%20recorded%20on%20the%20Control%20Unit%20(CU)%20is%20not%20visible%20at%20all%2C%20the%20voter%20has%20to%20be%20satisfied%20by%20the%20mere%20sound%20of%20a%20beep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20counting%20day%2C%20only%20the%20CUs%20are%20brought%20to%20the%20counting%20hall%20and%20the%20tally%20of%20votes%20is%20calculated%20by%20pressing%20the%20relevant%20button%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20candidates.%20Only%20the%20serial%20numbers%2C%20not%20the%20names%20of%20the%20candidates%20are%20visible%20on%20the%20CU.%20Further%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20directives%2C%20VVPAT%20slips%20are%20counted%20from%20only%20five%20randomly%20selected%20units%20in%20Assembly%20elections.%20For%20parliamentary%20elections%2C%20five%20units%20are%20chosen%20randomly%20from%20the%20Assembly%20segments%20of%20the%20constituency%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20tallying%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20count%20with%20the%20candidate-wise%20totals%20that%20the%20CU%20calculates.%20This%20random%20selection%20process%20is%20not%20visible%20to%20the%20counting%20agents%20(having%20served%20as%20a%20counting%20agent%20to%20an%20independent%20candidate%20in%20the%202020%20Delhi%20assembly%20elections%2C%20I%20know%20this%20for%20a%20fact).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20the%20transition%20is%20made%20from%20the%20starkly%20visual%20attributes%20of%20a%20paper-based%20voting%20and%20counting%20system%20to%20the%20present%20machine-mediated%20system%20(with%20only%20two%20very%20limited%20visual%20and%20even%20shorter%20audio%20feedback-%20beep!%20beep!%20Beep!)%2C%20the%20ECI%20has%20a%20more%20onerous%20duty%20of%20transparency%20towards%20the%20electorate.%20Convincing%20the%20voter%20places%20a%20much%20higher%20burden%20of%20proof%20than%20what%20the%20ECI%20is%20currently%20willing%20to%20discharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20answers%20to%20several%20of%20the%20100%20FAQs%20do%20not%20satisfactorily%20discharge%20this%20burden.%20Let%20us%20start%20with%20the%20most%20basic%20FAQs%20where%20the%20ECI%20has%20tried%20to%20explain%20how%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo%20works%2C%20internally.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20FAQs%20relating%20to%20signal%20flow%20(FAQs%20%232%2C%2039%2C%20and%2086)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20response%20to%20FAQ%20%232-%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EIn%20what%20way%20functioning%20of%20EVMs%20is%20different%20from%20conventional%20voting%20through%20paper%20ballots%3F%20Whether%20technical%20knowledge%20is%20required%20for%20casting%20vote%20through%20the%20EVM%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20ECI%20explains%20the%20process%20of%20electronic%20voting%20that%20I%20have%20summarised%20above%20and%20says%20that%20it%20is%20better%20than%20a%20paper%20ballot-based%20system%20which%20had%20problems%20like%20improper%20marking%20or%20smudging%20of%20ink.%20Further%2C%20the%20ECI%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EWhen%20the%20voter%20presses%20a%20button%20against%20the%20candidate%20of%20his%2Fher%20choice%20on%20Ballot%20Unit%2C%20a%20red%20LED%20glows%20against%20the%20chosen%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20button%20on%20BU.%20A%20paper%20slip%20showing%20the%20serial%20number%2C%20name%20and%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20candidate%20of%20his%2Fher%20choice%20is%20generated%20and%20is%20visible%20for%20about%207%20seconds%20through%20transparent%20window%20of%20VVPAT.%20Hence%20the%20voter%20is%20able%20to%20see%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprinted%20slip%E2%80%9D%20and%20verify%20that%20vote%20is%20cast%20as%20per%20his%2Fher%20choice.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20printed%20paper%20slip%20gets%20cut%20automatically%20and%20stored%20in%20sealed%20Drop%20box%20of%20VVPAT.%20A%20%3Cu%3Eloud%20BEEP%20is%20heard%20from%20the%20Control%20Unit%20which%20confirms%20that%20the%20vote%20is%20registered%20successfully%3C%2Fu%3E.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20FAQ%20%2339%20in%20response%20to%20the%20query-%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EIs%20it%20possible%20to%20vote%20more%20than%20once%20on%20an%20EVM%20by%20pressing%20the%20button%20again%20and%20again%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20explanation%20(reproduced%20below)%20about%20how%20the%20EVM%20behaves%20is%20at%20complete%20variance%20with%20the%20explanation%20given%20against%20FAQ%20%232%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ENo%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20vote%20more%20than%20once%20on%20an%20ECI-EVM%20by%20a%20particular%20voter.%20As%20soon%20as%20a%20particular%20button%20on%20the%20Ballot%20Unit%20is%20pressed%2C%20the%20vote%20is%20recorded%20for%20that%20particular%20candidate%20and%20a%20loud%20beep%20is%20emitted%20for%20officials%20and%20election%20agents%20to%20note%20that%20the%20vote%20%3Cu%3Ehas%20been%20completed%3C%2Fu%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20the%20complete%20absence%20of%20any%20reference%20to%20the%20VVPAT%20stage%20of%20the%20voting%20process%20in%20this%20reply.%20Those%20with%20unshakeable%20faith%20in%20the%20electronic%20voting%20system%20may%20claim%20this%20is%20just%20a%20legacy%20response%20from%20the%20times%20when%20EVMs%20were%20not%20paired%20with%20VVPATs%20at%20all%20and%20it%20must%20not%20be%20seen%20in%20isolation%20from%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20reply%20to%20FAQ%20%232.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20deployment%20of%20VVPAT%20units%20became%20mandatory%20only%20after%20the%202013%20directive%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%2C%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20%3Cem%3EDr.%20Subramanian%20Swamy%20vs%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Let%20us%20accept%20that%20reasoning%20temporarily%20and%20move%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFAQ%20%2386%20is%20a%20recent%20addition%20(January%202024)%2C%20not%20found%20in%20the%20much%20shorter%20FAQs%20list%20the%20ECI%20released%20in%20August%202023.%20The%20query%20is%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EHow%20does%20signal%2Fcommand%20flow%20between%20various%20units%20of%20EVM%20viz.%20BU%2C%20CU%20and%20VVPAT%3F%20Since%20the%20VVPAT%20is%20kept%20along%20with%20BU%20inside%20the%20voting%20compartment%20of%20the%20voter%2C%20does%20VVPAT%20receive%20any%20signal%2Fcommand%20from%20BU%20and%20vice-versa%3F%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3ETo%20this%2C%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20elaborate%20reply%20is%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EIn%20M3%20EVMs%2C%20CU%20always%20acts%20as%20Master%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20position%20in%20which%20it%20is%20placed%20or%20connected.%20BU%20and%20VVPAT%20act%20as%20Slave%20units%20in%20the%20connected%20network%2C%20which%20receive%20commands%20from%20CU%20to%20act%20as%20per%20the%20application%20programme.%20%3Cu%3EBU%20and%20VVPAT%20do%20not%20communicate%20with%20each%20other.%20It%20is%20the%20CU%20that%20communicates%20with%20both%20the%20BU%20and%20VVPAT%3C%2Fu%3E.%20%3Cu%3EWhen%20a%20voter%20presses%20a%20candidate%20button%20on%20BU%2C%20the%20BU%20sends%20the%20button%20number%20to%20CU%20and%20in%20turn%2C%20the%20CU%20communicates%20to%20VVPAT%20to%20print%20the%20slip%20of%20the%20corresponding%20button%20number%3C%2Fu%3E.%20%3Cu%3EOnly%20after%20printing%20and%20cutting%20of%20the%20printed%20VVPAT%20slip%2C%20the%20CU%20registers%20the%20vote%3C%2Fu%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EVotes%20are%20recorded%20only%20in%20CUs%20and%20not%20in%20BUs%20or%20VVPATs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E.%20When%20a%20particular%20Candidate%E2%80%99s%20button%20in%20BU%20is%20pressed%20by%20the%20voters%2C%20BU%20sends%20the%20button%20number%20to%20CU%20and%20CU%20commands%20printing%20of%20slip%20related%20to%20that%20button%20number%20to%20VVPAT.%20The%20VVPAT%20slip%20so%20printed%20remains%20visible%20to%20the%20voters%20for%20about%20seven%20seconds%20to%20verify%20their%20votes%20cast%20through%20the%20VVPAT%20display%20window.%20VVPAT%20then%20sends%20an%20acknowledgment%20to%20the%20CU%20to%20mark%20completion%20of%20printing%20of%20slip.%20The%20CU%20then%20initiates%20the%20cut%20of%20the%20printed%20slip%20and%20the%20slip%20falls%20in%20the%20sealed%20drop%20box%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20(Rules%2049A%20and%2049M%2C%20The%20Conduct%20of%20Elections%20Rules%2C%201961).%20After%20the%20successful%20completion%20of%20all%20these%20steps%2C%20i.e.%20printing%20and%20cutting%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20slips%2C%20the%20VVPAT%20sends%20an%20acknowledgement%20to%20the%20CU.%20Upon%20receiving%20the%20message%20from%20VVPAT%2C%20the%20CU%20records%20the%20vote%20electronically%20and%20emits%20a%20long%20BEEP.%20The%20BEEP%20marks%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20voting%20process%20for%20the%20voter.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20M3%20model%2C%20Master-Slave%20bus%20architecture%20is%20used.%20%3Cu%3EVVPAT%20can%20be%20connected%20anywhere%20in%20the%20EVM%20M3%20bus%3C%2Fu%3E.%20The%20Control%20Unit%20(CU)%20implements%20communication%2C%20command%20processing%2C%20handling%20of%20key%20operations%20and%20handling%20of%20all%20the%20commands%2Fresponses%20to%2Ffrom%20BU%20and%20VVPAT.%20The%20Master-Slave%20protocol%20is%20used%20to%20control%20access%20to%20the%20communication%20bus.%20Communication%20on%20the%20bus%20is%20initiated%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9CMaster%E2%80%9D%20(CU)%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9CCommand%E2%80%9D%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9CSlave%E2%80%9D%20(BU%20%26amp%3B%20VVPAT).%20%3Cu%3EThe%20%E2%80%9CSlave%E2%80%9D%20which%20is%20constantly%20monitoring%20the%20bus%20for%20%E2%80%9CCommands%E2%80%9D%20will%20recognize%20only%20the%20%E2%80%9CCommands%E2%80%9D%20addressed%20to%20it%20and%20will%20respond%20by%20performing%20an%20action%20and%20by%20returning%20a%20%E2%80%9CResponse%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fu%3E.%20Only%20the%20Master%20can%20initiate%20a%20command.%20%3Cu%3ECU%20is%20always%20the%20Master%20in%20the%20ECI%20M3%20EVM%20system%20setup.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20to%20FAQ%20%2386%20ends%20with%20a%20signal%20flow%20schematic%20and%20suggests%20that%20readers%20refer%20to%20Annexure-I%20as%20well%20for%20further%20clarity.%20Annexure-I%20contains%20a%20signal%20flow%20diagram%20(see%20%3Cem%3EImages%201%20%26amp%3B%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20below)%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20475px)%2085vw%2C%20475px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165011%2FImage-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22475%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165011%2FImage-1.jpg%20475w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165011%2FImage-1-300x220.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697650%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22349%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%201%3A%20Signal%20flow%20schematic%20under%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20answer%20to%20FAQ%20%2386%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165126%2Fimage-2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22716%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165126%2Fimage-2.png%20716w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165126%2Fimage-2-300x163.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697651%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22388%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%202%3A%20Signal%20flow%20diagram%20at%20Annexure-I%20to%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20FAQs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EII.%20What%20is%20problematic%20with%20these%20answers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20common%20knowledge%20that%20only%20two%20Union%20Government-owned%20public%20sector%20undertakings%20(CPSUs)%20namely%2C%20BEL%20(under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence)%20and%20ECIL%20(under%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy)%20have%20been%20manufacturing%20the%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs.%20According%20to%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20answer%20to%20FAQ%20%237%20they%20have%20a%20duopoly%20on%20the%20supply%20of%20these%20machines%20for%20parliamentary%20and%20assembly%20elections.%20However%2C%20few%20people%20know%20two%20related%20facts%20which%20the%20ECI%20has%20not%20bothered%20to%20mention%20in%20any%20of%20its%20FAQs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20in%202001%2C%20both%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20applied%20for%20the%20grant%20of%20exclusive%20patent%20rights%20under%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Patents%20Act%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3E1970%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20claiming%20that%20their%20EVMs%20are%20their%20unique%20invention%2Finnovation%20markedly%20different%20from%20the%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20that%20were%20in%20use%20in%20other%20countries.%20After%20due%20examination%20of%20their%20claims%20the%20Patent%20Office%2C%20Chennai%20granted%20patent%20rights%20to%20both%20CPSUs%20in%202006%20for%20a%20period%20of%2020%20years%20%E2%80%93%20the%20maximum%20duration%20permissible%20under%20the%20law.%20These%20patents%20expired%20in%202021%20(as%20per%20law%20the%2020-year%20period%20is%20calculated%20from%20the%20date%20of%20the%20patent%20application%20and%20not%20the%20date%20of%20the%20order%20granting%20the%20patent).%20How%20is%20exclusivity%20being%20maintained%20by%20the%20two%20CPSUs%20after%20the%20lapse%20of%20the%20EVM%20patents%20is%20a%20mystery%20because%20there%20is%20no%20provision%20in%20the%20patents%20law%20for%20extending%20the%20validity%20of%20a%20patent%20beyond%2020%20years%20(evergreening%20of%20a%20patent%20is%20not%20permitted%20under%20our%20law).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20patent-related%20documents%20are%20required%20to%20be%20publicly%20accessible%20to%20any%20person%20by%20law%2C%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20Controller%20General%20of%20Patents%2C%20Designs%20and%20Trademarks%20under%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20publishes%20all%20documents%20from%20the%20application%20stage%20to%20the%20stage%20of%20grant%20of%20the%20patent%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fipindia.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3Ededicated%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20patent%20application%2C%20complete%20specifications%20of%20and%20claims%20related%20to%20the%20invention%2Finnovation%20(what%20it%20is%20capable%20of%20doing%20and%20how)%20for%20which%20an%20applicant%20is%20seeking%20the%20patent%2C%20the%20drawings%20which%20visually%20portray%20the%20looks%20of%20the%20invention%2C%20corporate%20data%20about%20the%20applicant%20entity%2C%20details%20of%20the%20patent%20agent%20through%20whom%20the%20applicant%20interacts%20with%20the%20Patent%20Office%2C%20the%20report%20of%20the%20examiner%20who%20studies%20the%20claims%20and%20any%20amendments%20to%20the%20original%20documents%20submitted%20by%20the%20applicant%20etc.%20are%20all%20available%20through%20a%20very%20utilitarian%20database.%20If%20the%20patent%20is%20granted%20that%20order%20is%20also%20uploaded%20on%20this%20database%20along%20with%20a%20copy%20of%20its%20communication%20to%20the%20applicant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20transparency%20is%20an%20essential%20to%20enable%20any%20person%20to%20file%20an%20objection%20against%20the%20patent%20application%20or%20claim%20on%20the%20grounds%20permissible%20under%20the%20%3Cem%3EPatents%20Act%3C%2Fem%3E.%20If%20the%20objection%20is%20upheld%2C%20the%20patent%20application%20will%20be%20rejected.%20EVM%20patent-related%20documents%20continue%20to%20be%20accessible%20on%20this%20database%20despite%20the%20expiry%20of%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20patents.%20After%20the%20successful%20completion%20of%20the%20application%20process%2C%20the%20patent%20holder%20may%20deploy%20his%2Fher%2Ftheir%20invention%2Finnovation%20exclusively%20for%20commercial%20use%20unless%20he%2Fshe%2Fit%20voluntarily%20grants%20a%20license%20to%20any%20other%20entity%20for%20a%20similar%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20only%20BEL%20applied%20for%20a%20patent%20for%20the%20VVPAT%20machine%20in%20March%202018%20and%20received%20the%20patent%20order%20from%20the%20Chennai%20Patent%20Office%20in%20May%202022%20(after%20the%20completion%20of%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections).%20To%20the%20best%20of%20my%20knowledge%2C%20ECIL%E2%80%99s%20patent%20application%20for%20a%20VVPAT%20machine%20is%20not%20available%20on%20this%20database%2C%20so%20it%20may%20be%20presumed%20that%20there%20is%20some%20working%20arrangement%20between%20the%20two%20CPSUs%20for%20manufacturing%20the%20VVPAT%20machines.%20All%20the%20aforementioned%20documents%20and%20many%20more%20relating%20to%20the%20VVPAT%20patent%20which%20BEL%20secured%20are%20downloadable%20free%20of%20charge%20from%20this%20database%20(no%20you%20do%20not%20need%20an%20RTI%20application%20to%20seek%20access%20to%20these%20documents!).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20extract%20from%20the%20detailed%20drawings%20BEL%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patent%20Office%20in%20March%202019%20which%20shows%20the%20backend%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20machine%20is%20reproduced%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165428%2Fimage-3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165428%2Fimage-3.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165428%2Fimage-3-300x255.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165428%2Fimage-3-1024x871.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697653%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221021%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%203%3A%20Backend%20view%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20as%20per%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20drawing%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patent%20Office%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20above%20image%20clearly%20shows%20two%20ports%20that%20permit%20connection%20of%20the%20CU%20and%20BU%20units%20of%20the%20EVM%20to%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%E2%80%99s%20backend.%20In%20the%20early%20versions%20of%20VVPAT%20machines%2C%20there%20were%20two%20units-%20a%20printer%20that%20printed%20the%20choice%20of%20the%20voter%20on%20paper%20slips%20and%20the%20VSDU%20(visual%20status%20display%20unit)%20which%20would%20display%20the%20functional%20status%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20especially%20any%20errors%20detected%20in%20the%20printer.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20ECI%E2%80%99s%202018%20Status%20Paper%20on%20EVMs%2C%20in%20M3%20model%20of%20EVMs%20(which%20are%20currently%20in%20use%20all%20over%20the%20country)%2C%20VSDUs%20were%20integrated%20into%20the%20CU%20itself.%20This%20version%20of%20the%20EVM%20Manual%20has%20been%20replaced%20with%20subsequent%20versions%20and%20is%20unfortunately%20no%20longer%20displayed%20on%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20website.%20As%20I%20happened%20to%20download%20a%20copy%20in%202018%20itself%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20cite%20from%20this%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20according%20to%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feci.gov.in%2Ffiles%2Ffile%2F13911-manual-on-electronic-voting-machine-and-vvpat-edition-7-december-2022%2F%5C%22%3Elatest%20Manual%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%2C%20engineers%20of%20the%20two%20CPSUs%20who%20are%20tasked%20with%20the%20job%20of%20candidate-setting%20are%20instructed%20to%20connect%20the%20VVPAT%20with%20CU%20and%20BU%20with%20separate%20cables%20for%20this%20purpose%20(see%20%3Cem%3EImage%204%3C%2Fem%3E%20below).%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fcoochbehar.nic.in%2FAElection2021%2FTrainingModules%2FonEVMnVVPAT_tillDC.pdf%5C%22%3EBEL%E2%80%99s%20MSPPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20says%20that%20in%20order%20to%20commission%20the%20VVPAT%20it%20must%20be%20connected%20to%20the%20CU%20and%20BU%20individually%20(see%20%3Cem%3EImage%205%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebelow).%20So%2C%20there%20is%20no%20cable%20connection%20between%20the%20CU%20and%20BU%20at%20all.%20All%20communication%20is%20mediated%20through%20the%20bus%20architecture%20which%20is%20physically%20housed%20in%20the%20VVPAT%20unit.%20This%20is%20the%20inevitable%20and%20logical%20conclusion%20that%20one%20arrives%20at%20based%20on%20the%20information%20contained%20in%20the%20drawings%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20and%20the%20instructions%20of%20ECI%20and%20BEL%20mentioned%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165537%2FImage-4.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22908%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165537%2FImage-4.jpg%20908w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165537%2FImage-4-227x300.jpg%20227w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165537%2FImage-4-775x1024.jpg%20775w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697654%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165918%2FImage-5.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165918%2FImage-5.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165918%2FImage-5-300x208.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17165918%2FImage-5-1024x710.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697655%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22832%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%204%20%26amp%3B%205%3A%20Instructions%20for%20Engineers%20for%20candidate-setting%20in%20VVPATs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20logical%20conclusion%2C%20what%20do%20we%20make%20of%20this%20portion%20of%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20answer%20to%20FAQ%20%2386%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%3Cem%3EBU%20and%20VVPAT%20do%20not%20communicate%20with%20each%20other.%20It%20is%20the%20CU%20that%20communicates%20with%20both%20the%20BU%20and%20VVPAT.%20When%20a%20voter%20presses%20a%20candidate%20button%20on%20BU%2C%20the%20BU%20sends%20the%20button%20number%20to%20CU%20and%20in%20turn%2C%20the%20CU%20communicates%20to%20VVPAT%20to%20print%20the%20slip%20of%20the%20corresponding%20button%20number.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20then%20do%20the%20BU%20and%20CU%20communicate%20with%20each%20other%20when%20both%20are%20required%20to%20be%20connected%20only%20to%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20and%20not%20to%20each%20other%3F%20Is%20the%20%E2%80%98bus%20architecture%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20something%20like%20the%20bypass%20routes%20that%20are%20constructed%20on%20National%20Highways%20(like%20Agra%20bypass%2C%20Lucknow%20bypass%2C%20Chennai%20bypass%20etc.)%20to%20skirt%20around%20major%20cities%20and%20towns%20and%20travel%20faster%20to%20one%E2%80%99s%20destination%3F%20After%20the%20voter%20presses%20the%20button%20of%20choice%20on%20the%20BU%20is%20that%20signal%20somehow%20flowing%20to%20the%20CU%20unbeknownst%20to%20the%20VVPAT%20even%20though%20this%20communication%20is%20happening%20between%20the%20two%20units%20on%20the%20real%20estate%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%3F%20The%20ECI%20ought%20to%20explain%20how%20this%20magical%20signal%20flow%20takes%20place%20to%20lay%20voters%20like%20me%20who%20are%20neither%20hardware%20nor%20software%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20ending%20this%20writeup%2C%20another%20element%20of%20the%20answer%20to%20FAQs%20%232%20and%20%2386%20deserve%20critical%20examination.%20In%20response%20to%20FAQ%20%232%20the%20ECI%20says%2C%20after%20the%20voter%20presses%20the%20button%20of%20choice%20on%20the%20BU%2C%20the%20VVPAT%20unit%20gets%20into%20action%2C%20prints%20the%20slip%2C%20turns%20its%20light%20on%20for%20the%20voter%20to%20see%20and%20verify%20that%20his%2Fher%20choice%20has%20been%20correctly%20printed%2C%20cuts%20it%20and%20drops%20it%20into%20the%20drop%20box%20before%20switching%20the%20light%20off.%20Then%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ea%20loud%20BEEP%20is%20heard%20from%20the%20Control%20Unit%20which%20confirms%20that%20the%20vote%20is%20registered%20successfully%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20In%20response%20to%20FAQ%20%2386%2C%20the%20ECI%20explains%20how%20the%20CU%20is%20the%20Master%20and%20the%20BU%20and%20VVPATs%20are%20Slave%20units%20which%20receive%20commands%20from%20CU%20to%20act%20as%20per%20the%20application%20programme.%20Further%20the%20explanation%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%3Cem%3EThe%20Master-Slave%20protocol%20is%20used%20to%20control%20access%20to%20the%20communication%20bus.%20Communication%20on%20the%20bus%20is%20initiated%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9CMaster%E2%80%9D%20(CU)%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9CCommand%E2%80%9D%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9CSlave%E2%80%9D%20(BU%20%26amp%3B%20VVPAT).%20%3Cu%3EThe%20%E2%80%9CSlave%E2%80%9D%20which%20is%20constantly%20monitoring%20the%20bus%20for%20%E2%80%9CCommands%E2%80%9D%20will%20recognize%20only%20the%20%E2%80%9CCommands%E2%80%9D%20addressed%20to%20it%20and%20will%20respond%20by%20performing%20an%20action%20and%20by%20returning%20a%20%E2%80%9CResponse%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fu%3E.%20Only%20the%20Master%20can%20initiate%20a%20command.%20%3Cu%3ECU%20is%20always%20the%20Master%20in%20the%20ECI%20M3%20EVM%20system%20setup.%3C%2Fu%3E%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20is%20the%20set%20protocol%2C%20what%20do%20we%20make%20of%20these%20assertions%20of%20BEL%20before%20the%20Patents%20Office%3F%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%5B0030%5D%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20an%20aspect%2C%20%3Cu%3Ethe%20apparatus%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cu%3E%5BVVPAT%5D%20%3Cem%3Ecan%20be%20functionally%20or%20physically%20integrated%20with%20the%20ballot%20unit%20of%20EVM%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20the%20physical%20artefact%20of%20which%20provides%20the%20functionality%20of%20both%20the%20units.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%5B0031%5D%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20an%20aspect%2C%20%3Cu%3Ethe%20apparatus%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cu%3E%5BVVPAT%5D%20%3Cem%3Ecan%20be%20functionally%20or%20physically%20integrated%20as%20a%20single%20unit%20providing%20functionality%20of%20VVPAT%2C%20control%20unit%20and%20ballot%20unit%20of%20EVM%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%5B00120%5D%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20an%20aspect%2C%20%3Cu%3Eif%20the%20printing%20is%20not%20successful%20for%20any%20reason%2C%20then%20the%20vote%20cast%20cannot%20be%20stored%3C%2Fu%3E%2C%20and%20the%20VVPAT%20system%20can%20be%20put%20in%20an%20error%20mode%20and%20prevented%20from%20further%20use%20in%20the%20election%20process.%20This%20ensures%20number%20of%20votes%20stored%20in%20the%20CU%20and%20the%20number%20of%20slips%20in%20the%20VVPAT%20is%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%5B00125%5D%20In%20an%20aspect%2C%20proposed%20system%20%5BVVPAT%5D%20can%2C%20after%20successful%20printing%2C%20displaying%20and%20storing%20a%20ballot%20slip%20can%20%3Cu%3Esend%20an%20acknowledgement%20of%20successful%20operation%20to%20the%20corresponding%20EVM%3C%2Fu%3E.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParagraphs%20%230030%20and%200031%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Complete%20Specifications%20submitted%20while%20seeking%20grant%20of%20a%20patent%20and%20paragraphs%20%2300120%20and%2000125%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Detailed%20description%20of%20the%20VVPAT-related%20drawings%20attached%20to%20these%20Complete%20Specifications%20(see%20%3Cem%3EImages%206%2C%207%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%20%26amp%3B%208%3C%2Fem%3E%20below).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20BEL%20claimed%20before%20the%20Patents%20Office%20that%20the%20VVPAT%20can%20be%20integrated%20with%20the%20BU%20physically%20and%20not%20the%20CU%20(as%20is%20the%20case%20from%20the%20evidence%20presented%20above).%20Second%2C%20even%20though%20according%20to%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20reply%20to%20FAQ%20%2386%20the%20CU%20is%20initially%20aware%20of%20the%20choice%20made%20by%20the%20voter%2C%20according%20to%20BEL%20it%20can%20record%20the%20same%20only%20if%20the%20printing%20process%20is%20successful.%20If%20the%20printing%20process%20is%20unsuccessful%2C%20the%20CU%20cannot%20record%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20choice%20even%20if%20it%20somehow%20had%20prior%20knowledge%20of%20the%20same.%20In%20this%20respect%20at%20least%2C%20the%20VVPAT%20must%20be%20seen%20as%20acting%20like%20a%20Master%20and%20the%20CU%20as%20a%20Slave%20which%20records%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20choice%20digitally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170054%2FImage-6.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22849%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170054%2FImage-6.jpg%20849w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170054%2FImage-6-212x300.jpg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17170054%2FImage-6-724x1024.jpg%20724w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697656%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-capti