k%2C%20'just%20make%20sure%20you%20get%20up%20and%20down%20the%20wicket'...%20that%20was%20gamesmanship%20there%2C%20wasn't%20it%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20went%20on%20to%20add.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%2C%20however%2C%20took%20full%20blame%20of%20the%20penalty%20and%20revealed%20that%20he%20wasn't%20aware%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Indian%20team%20had%20received%20warning%20for%20running%20on%20the%20pitch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20clearly%20warned%20some%20of%20our%20batters%20(on%20Thursday)%20for%20running%20on%20the%20pitch.%20I%20was%20aware%20of%20it%2C%20but%20my%20poor%20motor%20skills%20didn't%20allow%20me%20to%20get%20off%20the%20pitch%20in%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said%20at%20the%20post-day%20press%20conference%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20also%20responded%20to%20Cook's%20allegations%20in%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20English%20media%20and%20players%20think%20it%20was%20on%20purpose%2C%20it%20wasn't.%20If%20that's%20how%20they%20want%20to%20treat%20it%2C%20so%20be%20it.%20I%20went%20to%20(on-field%20umpires)%20Joel%20(Wilson)%20and%20Kumar%20(Dharmasena)%20and%20said%20'that's%20pure%20poor%20motor%20skills.%20If%20I%20was%20any%20better%2C%20I%20would%20have%20been%20in%20the%20Olympics.%20Why%20play%20cricket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20made%20history%20by%20becoming%20the%20second%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20bowler%20ever%20to%20take%20500%20Test%20wickets%20but%20it%20was%20not%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20grabbed%20headlines%20regarding%20the%20veteran%20spinner%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2037-year-old%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20squad%20for%20the%20ongoing%20match%20as%20he%20flew%20back%20to%20Chennai%20to%20attend%20to%20his%20ill%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20gaining%20a%20five-run%20advantage%20without%20a%20ball%20being%20bowled%2C%20England%20were%20all%20out%20for%20319%20as%20India%20(445)%20took%20a%20126-run%20lead%20in%20the%20first