however%2C%20met%20in%20Washington%20shortly%20after%20the%20contentious%20allegations%20were%20aired%2C%20when%20the%20Indian%20foreign%20minister%20was%20in%20United%20States%20to%20attend%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly.%20This%20meeting%20was%20unannounced%20and%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-canada-jaishankar-melanie-joly-washington-meeting%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eneither%20officially%20denied%20nor%20confirmed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20either%20Ottawa%20or%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20four%20months%20later%2C%20both%20countries%20announced%20their%20meeting%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20Munich%20Security%20Conference%20on%20Friday%2C%20February%2016.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20conversation%20understandably%20focused%20on%20the%20present%20state%20of%20our%20bilateral%20ties.%20Was%20also%20useful%20to%20exchange%20views%20on%20the%20global%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FDrSJaishankar%2Fstatus%2F1758602722528379278%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Indian%20external%20affairs%20minister%20Jaishankar%20posted%20on%20X%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmelaniejoly%2Fstatus%2F1758668177163292804%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECanadian%20foreign%20minister%20Melanie%20Joly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20w%3C%2Fspan%3Erote%20on%20X%3Cspan%3E%20that%20they%20had%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfrank%20discussion%20on%20Canada-India%20relations%20and%20the%20current%20global%20issues%2C%20including%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20illegal%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Advancements%E2%80%99%20after%20tension%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20September%2019%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20stood%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20and%20announced%20that%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%20allegations%E2%80%9D%20of%20Indian%20government%20agents%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20national%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20whom%20New%20Delhi%20describes%20as%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20and%20Canada%20had%20each%20expelled%20a%20senior%20diplomat%2C%20but%20New%20Delhi%20went%20further%20to%20stop%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadian%20nationals.%20India%20also%20forced%20Canada%20to%20downsize%20its%20diplomatic%20presence%20by%20calling%20for%20reciprocity%20in%20the%20size%20of%20embassies%20and%20other%20outposts%20in%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20countries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20months%20after%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20announcement%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-assassination-plot-india-enquiry-committee-set-up%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUS%20prosecutors%20unsealed%20charges%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20against%20an%20Indian%20national%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20which%20linked%20an%20unnamed%20government%20official%20to%20the%20foiled%20attempt%20to%20murder%20a%20Khalistani%20group%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20in%20New%20York%20by%20hiring%20a%20hitman.%20The%20November%20indictment%20also%20connected%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing%20in%20June%202023%20with%20the%20alleged%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20the%20reaction%20to%20Canada%2C%20India%20quickly%20set%20up%20a%20high-level%20committee%20to%20probe%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20US%20investigators.%20However%2C%20no%20announcement%20about%20the%20result%20of%20the%20probe%20has%20been%20made%20so%20far.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20outgoing%20Canadian%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Jody%20Thomas%20had%20claimed%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cadvancements%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20relationship.%20She%20had%20also%20said%20in%20her%20interview%20to%20Canadian%20media%20that%20India%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccooperating%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20investigation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20a%20week%20later%2C%20the%20Indian%20high%20commissioner%20to%20Canada%2C%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Verma%20contradicted%20Thomas%20and%20said%20that%20New%20Delhi%20was%20not%20cooperating%20as%20it%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-india-nsa-jody-thomas-sanjay-verma-nijjar%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eyet%20to%20receive%20any%20evidence%20from%20Canadian%20authorities%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20same%20day%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ourcommons.ca%2Fdocumentviewer%2Fen%2F44-1%2FFAAE%2Fmeeting-92%2Fevidence%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20Canadian%20House%20of%20Common%E2%80%99s%20standing%20committee%20on%20foreign%20affairs%20and%20international%20development%20held%20a%20hearing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20where%20a%20senior%20Canadian%20diplomat%20noted%20that%20information%20from%20the%20police%20investigation%20had%20not%20yet%20been%20shared.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConspiracy%20and%20inquiries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWeldon%20Epp%2C%20the%20Canadian%20foreign%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20assistant%20deputy%20minister%20for%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20told%20lawmakers%20that%20the%20Indian%20position%20has%20been%20that%20%E2%80%9Cuntil%20they%20receive%20evidence%20from%20a%20police%20investigation%2C%20they%20will%20reserve%20their%20right%20as%20to%20how%20they%20will%20respond%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20inaccurate%20to%20say%20that%20while%20that%20investigation%20is%20still%20under%20way%2C%20the%20RCMP%20is%20not%20directly%20engaging%20the%20high%20commissioner%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20on%20February%205.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police%20(RCMP)%20is%20the%20primary%20investigative%20body%20for%20the%20case.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20Jaishankar%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fone-has-provided-inputs-another-hasnt-jaishankar-on-indias-differing-responses-to-us-canada%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ejustified%20India%E2%80%99s%20differing%20reaction%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20US%20and%20Canada%20by%20arguing%20that%20only%20one%20of%20them%20has%20given%20%E2%80%9Cspecific%20evidence%20or%20inputs%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20senior%20Canadian%20foreign%20ministry%20official%20said%20that%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20Canadian%20and%20American%20inquiries%20were%20different%20as%20one%20was%20a%20murder%2C%20while%20another%20was%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20hire%20a%20hitman.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%20the%20legal%20processes%20in%20US%20and%20Canada%20were%20very%20different.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20possibility%20for%20an%20early%20narrative%20and%20the%20disclosure%20of%20evidence%20through%20an%20indictment%20in%20the%20U.S.%20differs%20quite%20significantly%20from%20the%20legal%20process%20in%20Canada%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Epp.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinflection%20point%20in%20a%20Canadian%20investigation%2C%20such%20that%20detailed%20information%20supporting%20the%20investigation%20can%20be%20released%20to%20the%20public%20or%20a%20foreign%20government%2C%20comes%20at%20a%20later%20stage%E2%80%9D.%20He%20added%20that%20due%20to%20the%20disclosure%20of%20the%20US%20indictment%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20clear%20link%20being%20described%20by%20the%20evidence%20provided%20to%20date%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Asking%20questions%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDescribing%20the%20India%20setting%20up%20the%20%E2%80%9Cindependent%20high-level%20committee%E2%80%9D%20in%20response%20to%20US%20claims%20as%20a%20positive%20step%2C%20Epp%20observed%20that%20when%20investigation%20reaches%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccomparable%20inflection%20point%E2%80%9D%20in%20Canada%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20information%20will%20be%20available%20for%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20its%20high-level%20committee%20to%20consider%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Canadian%20diplomat%20also%20told%20lawmakers%20that%20Ottawa%20was%20in%20%E2%80%9Cintensive%E2%80%9D%20conversations%20with%20%E2%80%9Clike-minded%E2%80%9D%20allies%2C%20like%20United%20States%20and%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20over%20this%20ongoing%20challenge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20three%20countries%2C%20the%20two%20partners%20you%20named%20and%20Canada%2C%20have%20large%20diaspora%20communities%20that%20have%20been%20targets%20of%20transnational%20crime.%20There%20have%20been%20challenges%20that%20affect%20these%20communities.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20concern%20for%20domestic%20security%20as%20well%20as%20for%20engaging%20India%20on%20addressing%20those%20domestic%20matters%20that%20may%20play%20out%20differently%20in%20our%20legal%20systems%20than%20they%20do%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Epp%20as%20per%20the%20transcript.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20indicated%20that%20Ottawa%20had%20worked%20with%20the%20two%20countries%20to%20%E2%80%9Cask%20questions%20of%20our%20Indian%20colleagues%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20raise%20these%20questions%2C%20for%20Canada%20to%20raise%20them%2C%20to%20receive%20an%20official%20position%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20to%20hear%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20including%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20that%20they%20will%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdefinitely%20look%20into%E2%80%9D%20any%20evidence%20and%20hold%20people%20accountable%20if%20there%E2%80%99s%20evidence%20provided.%20Working%20with%20our%20partners%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20have%20to%20continue%20to%20raise%20these%20issues%20and%20have%20those%20conversations%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Epp.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20issue%20of%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20claims%20about%20activities%20of%20Khalistani%20groups%20in%20those%20three%20countries%20was%20also%20part%20of%20these%20conversations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6it%20is%20true%20that%20there%20have%20been%20discussions%2C%20both%20between%20our%20partners%20and%20India%20but%20also%20between%20our%20partners%E2%80%94between%20us%2C%20the%20U.K.%20and%20the%20U.S.%E2%80%94because%20we%20are%20all%20dealing%20with%20some%20similar%20impacts%20of%20differences%20between%20our%20legal%20systems%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20just%20say%2C%20and%20that%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20allegations%20of%20terrorism%20and%20extremism%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESensationalising%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20also%20complained%20publicly%20that%20Canada%20had%20gone%20public%20over%20its%20allegations%20despite%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20request%20for%20sharing%20information.%20While%20Trudeau%20had%20raised%20the%20matter%20directly%20with%20his%20Indian%20counterpart%20during%20the%20G-20%20summit%2C%20other%20senior%20Canadian%20officials%20had%20also%20visited%20New%20Delhi%20earlier.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20answer%20to%20repeated%20questions%20regarding%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20publicly%20disclose%20the%20accusations%2C%20Epp%20reaffirmed%20its%20necessity%2C%20citing%20an%20imminent%20publication%20by%20a%20prominent%20Canadian%20newspaper.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20answer%20your%20question%2C%20you%20can%20imagine%20it%E2%80%99s%20rather%20implausible%2C%20knowing%20the%20media%20was%20about%20to%20release%20the%20sensational%20story%2C%20that%20the%20government%20would%20simply%20choose%20not%20to%20comment.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%20as%20it%20has%20been%20previously%20described%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Minister%20Leblanc%2C%20was%20meant%20to%20address%20a%20concerned%20Canadian%20public%20and%20reassure%20them%20about%20what%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20approach%20would%20be%20in%20addressing%20this%20issue%20and%20how%20the%20government%20had%20already%20been%20actively%20involved%2C%20including%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20raising%20it%20personally%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20at%20the%20G20%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20also%20criticised%20Canada%20over%20concerns%20that%20it%20was%20giving%20space%20to%20Khalistani%20extremism%20and%20ignored%20repeated%20requests%20for%20extradition%20of%20proscribed%20terrorists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Epp%20argued%20that%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbody%20of%20ongoing%20requests%E2%80%9D%20from%20India%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cevidentiary%20threshold%20in%20Canadian%20law%20is%20not%20met%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20despite%20the%20frosty%20political%20relations%2C%20both%20countries%20have%20asserted%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Flok-sabha.htm%3Fdtl%2F37450%2Fquestion%2Bno2264%2Bindian%2Btrade%2Brelations%2Bwith%2Bcanada%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etrade%20ties%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20remained%20unaffected.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708167112000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17161843%2FScreenshot-2024-02-17-at-4.18.09.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-canada-foreign-ministers-nijjar-jaishankar-melanie-joly%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%