%20Tata%20Motors%20are%20introducing%20budget-friendly%20electric%20SUVs%20and%20sedans%20with%20impressive%20ranges%20and%20cutting-edge%20features.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20Poll%20Official%20Resigns%2C%20Accepts%20%26quot%3BWrongdoing%26quot%3B%20In%20Elections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20Pakistani%20bureaucrat%20on%20Saturday%20alleged%20that%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20and%20the%20chief%20justice%20were%20involved%20in%20poll%20rigging%20in%20the%20recent%20election%20as%20he%20resigned%20from%20his%20post%2C%20taking%20the%20%26quot%3Bresponsibility%20for%20all%20this%20wrongdoing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Rawalpindi%20Commissioner%20Liaquat%20Ali%20Chattha's%20remarks%20came%20amidst%20jailed%20former%20prime%20minister%20Imran%20Khan's%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20party%20began%20nationwide%20protests%20against%20alleged%20rigging%20and%20stealing%20of%20its%20mandate%20in%20the%20February%208%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20at%20the%20Rawalpindi%20Cricket%20Stadium%2C%20Liaquat%20Ali%20Chattha%20said%20the%20candidates%20who%20were%20%26quot%3Blosing%26quot%3B%20the%20elections%20%26quot%3Bwere%20made%20to%20win%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20taking%20the%20responsibility%20for%20all%20this%20wrongdoing%20and%20telling%20you%20that%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20and%20the%20chief%20justice%20are%20also%20completely%20involved%20in%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20Dawn%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiaquat%20Ali%20Chattha%20resigned%20from%20his%20office%20after%20%26quot%3Baccepting%20responsibility%26quot%3B%20for%20manipulation%20of%20poll%20results%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiaquat%20Ali%20Chattha%20said%20%26quot%3Bstabbing%20the%20country%20in%20its%20back%20does%20not%20let%26quot%3B%20him%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20should%20be%20punished%20for%20the%20injustice%20I%20have%20done%20and%20others%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20this%20injustice%20should%20also%20be%20punished%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20bureaucrat%20said%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bpressure%26quot%3B%20on%20him%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20he%20contemplated%20suicide%20but%20then%20resolved%20to%20present%20matters%20before%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20my%20request%20to%20the%20entire%20bureaucracy%20to%20not%20do%20anything%20wrong%20for%20all%20these%20politicians%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%20(ECP)%20has%20strongly%20rejected%20the%20allegations%20Chattha%20has%20made%20against%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20statement%2C%20it%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%20strongly%20rejects%20the%20allegations%20levelled%20by%20the%20Commissioner%20Rawalpindi%20on%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20or%20the%20election%20commission%20and%20no%20official%20of%20the%20election%20commission%20never%20issued%20any%20instructions%20regarding%20changing%20the%20election%20results%20to%20the%20Commissioner%20Rawalpindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeither%20is%20the%20commissioner%20of%20any%20division%20ever%20appointed%20as%20a%20DRO%2C%20RO%20or%20presiding%20officer%2C%20nor%20do%20they%20ever%20play%20a%20direct%20role%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20elections.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20it%20said%20that%20the%20matter%20would%20be%20investigated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Punjab%20caretaker%20Information%20Minister%20Amir%20Mir%20has%20also%20%26quot%3Brejected%26quot%3B%20the%20claims%20of%20manipulation%20of%20election%20results%20made%20by%20Liaquat%20Ali%20Chattha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20Geo%20News%2C%2