r-malta-mediterrane-film-festival-1235914603%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Ffestivals%2Fteresa-cavina-artistic-director-malta-mediterrane-film-festival-1235914603%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telegram%20Continues%20to%20Be%20the%20Chosen%20Medium%20for%20Hindutva%20Hate%20Speech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17154313%2FUntitled-design-1-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20January%2022%2C%20in%20what%20can%20be%20described%20as%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20moments%20of%20Hindutva%20triumphalism%20in%20a%20decade%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20unveiled%20the%20Ram%20idol%20in%20Ayodhya.%20Describing%20the%20temple%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20peace%2C%20harmony%2C%20and%20integration%20of%20all%20Indians%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20the%20moment%20illustrates%20the%20maturity%20of%20Indians.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20suggest%20that%20the%20temple%20will%20take%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20development%20journey%20to%20new%20heights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20conversations%20around%20the%20event%20on%20many%20groups%20of%20his%20supporters%20on%20the%20messaging%20app%20Telegram%20belies%20this%20supposed%20message%20of%20peace%20and%20harmony.%20Shortly%20before%20and%20after%20the%20inauguration%2C%20these%20Telegram%20groups%20unleashed%20a%20flood%20of%20hate%20messages%2C%20fake%20news%2C%20and%20political%20propaganda%20targeting%20Muslims%20and%20opposition%20parties%2C%20and%20representing%20the%20event%20as%20one%20that%20can%20start%20off%20the%20process%20of%20the%20demolition%20of%20more%20mosques.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20such%20message%20in%20a%20channel%20called%20Samaj%2C%20with%20around%20700%20subscribers%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETbh%20ab%20mullo%20ka%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Efuture%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20h%20nhi%20india%20me.%20kuch%20tym%20baad%20khule%20nhi%20dikhenge%20ye%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETranslated%2C%20it%20means%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20be%20honest%20there%20is%20no%20future%20of%20Muslims%20in%20India.%20They%20will%20not%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20open%20after%20some%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlgorithm%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20reporter%20tracked%20at%20least%2080%20such%20Telegram%20channels%2C%20which%20together%20have%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20subscribers%20and%20found%20that%20Telegram%E2%80%99s%20automated%20%E2%80%98suggestions%E2%80%99%20also%20aided%20the%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telegram%20algorithm%20works%20in%20a%20way%20that%20ensures%20that%20if%20you%20join%20two%20or%20three%20of%20these%20channels%2C%20a%20suggestion%20pops%20up%20with%20a%20link%20to%20join%20other%20channels%20of%20the%20same%20kind%2C%20making%20it%20easy%20for%20one%20to%20find%20like-minded%20channels.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20gain%20insight%20into%20how%20Telegram%20plays%20a%20unique%20role%20compared%20to%20other%20platforms%20in%20shaping%20debates%20and%20pushing%20propaganda%2C%20the%20reporter%20interviewed%20Professor%20Mohan%20J.%20Dutta.%20Dutta%20is%20Chair%20Professor%20of%20Communication%20at%20Massey%20University%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20and%20has%20studied%20far-right%20trends%20extensively.%20His%20work%20also%20focuses%20on%20the%20online%20Hindutva%20hate%20ecosystem.%20He%20has%20authored%20a%20series%20of%20research%20papers%20on%20cultural%20Hindutva%20and%20Islamophobia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhate-speech-bjp-anti-muslim-2023%5C%22%3E80%25%20of%20Anti-Muslim%20Hate%20Speech%20in%202023%20Was%20Delivered%20in%20BJP-Ruled%20States%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20how%20is%20Telegram%20different%20from%20other%20social%20media%20platforms%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20shaping%20debates%20and%20pushing%20propaganda%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDutta%20says%20that%20the%20answer%20lies%20in%20Telegram%E2%80%99s%20architecture.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20functions%20as%20a%20broadcasting%20channel%2C%20allowing%20for%20the%20rapid%20dissemination%20of%20messages%20to%20a%20large%20audience%2C%20including%20calls%20to%20violence%20and%20the%20organization%20of%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafety%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDoes%20Telegram%20afford%20more%20impunity%20to%20hate-mongers%20compared%20to%20other%20platforms%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDutta%20believes%20that%20the%20answer%20is%20not%20straight.%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20a%20higher%20degree%20of%20anonymity%20compared%20to%20platforms%20like%20WhatsApp%2C%20Telegram%20provides%20greater%20protection%20for%20hate%20influencers.%20Additionally%2C%20content%20on%20Telegram%20can%20easily%20become%20cross-platform%20material%2C%20further%20disseminating%20it%20on%20other%20platforms%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20is%20it%20that%20Hindutva%20groups%20gravitate%20towards%20Telegram%3F%20Here%2C%20Dutta%20feels%20that%20the%20sense%20of%20community%20it%20fosters%2C%20along%20with%20the%20assurance%20of%20safety%2C%20offers%20impunity%20to%20them.%20%E2%80%9COn%20X%2C%20for%20example%2C%20exposure%20is%20broader%20since%20it%20is%20a%20public%20platform.%20Thus%2C%20my%20observation%20is%20that%20the%20Hindutva%20ecosystem%20is%20very%20comfortable%20disseminating%20hate%20on%20Telegram%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Samaj%2C%20the%20above-mentioned%20channel%2C%20conversation%20ranges%20from%20casually%20sexist%20to%20deeply%20offensive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESomeone%20shares%20a%20video%20showing%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Satabdi%20Roy%2C%20where%20she%20is%20heard%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20(the%20BJP)%20say%20that%20they%20give%20homes%20to%20those%20who%20are%20below%20the%20poverty%20line.%20Then%20is%20Ram%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20admin%20of%20the%20channel%20starts%20the%20conversation%20by%20saying%20Roy%20%E2%80%9Cbelongs%20to%20the%20street%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20others%20follow%20with%20deeply%20misogynistic%20abuses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20one%20person%20replies%20to%20the%20message%20and%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBJP%20is%20playing%20with%20Hindu%E2%80%99s%20faith%20to%20gain%20votes%20and%20has%20made%20the%20masses%20rationally%20dumb%20and%20deaf%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20is%20assailed%20with%20abuses%20and%20asked%20to%20shut%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVisual%20vehicles%20of%20hatred%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20member%20sends%20a%20collection%20of%20stickers.%20One%20sticker%20depicts%20men%20with%20beards%20and%20skull%20caps%20locked%20inside%20a%20concentration%20camp%20with%20%E2%80%98New%20Madarsa%E2%80%99%20written%20on%20it.%20A%20man%20as%20the%20infamous%20%E2%80%98Pepe%20the%20frog%E2%80%99%20figure%20is%20in%20fatigues%2C%20with%20the%20symbol%20%E2%80%98om%E2%80%99%20on%20it.%20He%20is%20seen%20pressing%20the%20green%20button.%20Locked%20men%20are%20screaming%20and%20the%20Pepe%20figure%20is%20smoking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sticker%20is%20credited%20to%20%E2%80%98livingdadream%E2%80%99.%20A%20search%20of%20this%20username%20on%20Google%20takes%20you%20to%20an%20X%20account%20that%20has%20posted%20many%20%E2%80%98Pepe%20the%20frog%E2%80%99%20memes%20that%20depict%20the%20annihilation%20of%20Muslims%2C%20Nazi%20style.%20In%20one%20meme%20posted%20on%20X%20by%20this%20account%2C%20a%20Hindu%20man%20with%20a%20Swastika%20printed%20on%20his%20military%20uniform%20is%20holding%20a%20Muslim%20by%20his%20neck.%20Caption%20says%20%E2%80%9CDesh%20ke%20musalmano%20ko%2C%20goli%20maaro%20salo%20ko%20(kill%20the%20muslims%20of%20the%20country)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20photos%20and%20stickers%20are%20frequently%20posted%20in%20these%20channels%20by%20various%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20295px)%2085vw%2C%20295px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17152428%2FScreenshot-2024-02-17-at-3.24.13%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22295%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17152428%2FScreenshot-2024-02-17-at-3.24.13%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201020w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17152428%2FScreenshot-2024-02-17-at-3.24.13%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x300.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17152428%2FScreenshot-2024-02-17-at-3.24.13%25E2%2580%25AFPM-150x150.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697630%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22296%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESome%20of%20the%20anti-Muslim%20stickers%20and%20memes%20frequently%20shared%20in%20Hindutva%20Telegram%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Dutta%20feels%20that%20Telegram%20is%20often%20the%20space%20where%20hate%20groups%20can%20cross-fertilise%20and%20cross-pollinate%20ideas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTelegram%20is%20widely%20used%20by%20far-right%20hate%20groups%20globally%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Proud%20Boys%20group%2C%20who%20stormed%20the%20Capitol%20in%20the%20USA.There%20is%20a%20significant%20intersection%20between%20the%20far-right%20white%20supremacist%20movement%20and%20the%20far-right%20Hindutva%20movement.%20They%20borrow%20memes%20and%20messaging%20from%20each%20other%2C%20including%20calls%20for%20extreme%20violence.%20Islamophobia%20is%20where%20they%20intersect.%20There%20are%20two%20aspects%20to%20it.%20One%20is%20framing%20Muslims%20as%20%E2%80%9Cothers%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20threat%2C%20and%20constructing%20them%20in%20dehumanizing%20language%2C%20using%20that%20as%20a%20basis%20to%20call%20for%20extreme%20violence%20and%20genocide.%20The%20other%20aspect%20where%20they%20intersect%20is%20extreme%20misogyny%20and%20toxic%20masculinity%2C%20using%20demeaning%20language%20and%20calling%20for%20sexual%20violence%20against%20Muslim%20women%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Hindutva%E2%80%9D%E2%80%99%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20177px)%2085vw%2C%20177px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17152542%2FScreenshot-2024-02-17-at-3.24.39%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22177%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17152542%2FScreenshot-2024-02-17-at-3.24.39%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%20466w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17152542%2FScreenshot-2024-02-17-at-3.24.39%25E2%2580%25AFPM-139x300.png%20139w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697631%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22383%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20screengrab%20showing%20the%20reporting%20mechanism%20on%20Telegram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Telegram%20user%20can%20report%20a%20particular%20post%2Fmessage%20in%20the%20following%20categories%3A%20spam%2C%20violence%2C%20child%20abuse%2C%20illegal%20drugs%2C%20personal%20details%2C%20and%20pornography.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20mechanism%20to%20report%20a%20particular%20content%20for%20hate%20speech%20or%20dehumanisation.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20there%20is%20an%20%E2%80%98Other%E2%80%99%20option%20where%20you%20have%20to%20provide%20details%20manually%2C%20it%20does%20not%20offer%20any%20option%20to%20select%20the%20relevant%20problematic%20post%20%E2%80%93%20the%20report%20needs%20to%20be%20against%20the%20channel%20in%20general.%20The%20reporter%20reported%20at%20least%20five%20posts%20in%20five%20different%20Hindutva%20Telegram%20channels%20using%20the%20%E2%80%98Other%E2%80%99%20option%20providing%20details%20of%20why%20the%20post%20is%20hate%20speech.%20The%20posts%20are%20still%20present.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Dutta%20says%20that%20with%20X%20and%20Meta%2C%20there%20is%20at%20least%20access%20to%20a%20content%20moderation%20system%20%E2%80%9Cwhere%20you%20can%20raise%20a%20complaint%2C%20and%20you%20know%20how%20to%20do%20so.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTelegram%20is%20primarily%20a%20dissemination%20channel%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20really%20provide%20a%20feedback%20mechanism%20in%20that%20way.%20Therefore%2C%20content%20moderation%20is%20much%20weaker%20on%20Telegram%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708162214000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17154313%2FUntitled-design-1-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Ftelegram-continues-to-be-the-chosen-medium-for-hindutva-hate-speech%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hate%20speech%20targeting%20Muslims%2C%20women%20and%20minorities%20flood%20channels.%20Where%20does%20the%20impunity%20come%20from%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Ftelegram-continues-to-be-the-chosen-medium-for-hindutva-hate-speech%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japan's%20new%20flagship%20rocket%20reaches%20orbit%20in%20key%20test%