rofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20ongoing%20third%20Test%20against%20England.%20Ashwin%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20squad%20midway%20of%20the%20contest%2C%20flying%20back%20to%20Chennai%20to%20attend%20to%20his%20ill%20mother.%20India%20have%20brought%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Devdutt%20Padikkal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F110591-devdutt-padikkal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDevdutt%20Padikkal%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20substitute%20fielder%2C%20but%20he%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20bat%20or%20bowl%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20match.%20India%20are%20a%20player%20down%20with%20just%20four%20regular%20bowlers%20in%20their%20arsenal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumble%20feels%20while%20it%20is%20harsh%20to%20lose%20a%20matchwinner%20like%20Ashwin%2C%20India%20will%20have%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20plan%20to%20contain%20the%20England%20batters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20tough%20when%20a%20match-winner%20like%20Ashwin%20misses%20out%20on%20a%20big%20day%20when%20he%20was%20needed.%20We%20saw%20the%20damage%20he%20can%20do%2C%20picked%20up%20his%20500th%20Test%20wicket.%20But%20India%20will%20have%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20plan%20to%20get%20England%20out%20because%20they're%20going%20to%20score%20runs%2C%26quot%3B%20Kumble%20told%20the%20broadcasters%20ahead%20of%20the%20start%20of%20play%20on%20Day%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumble%20emphasised%20that%20Jadeja's%20role%2C%20along%20with%20the%20pacers%2C%20will%20become%20more%20crucial%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20Ashwin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fast-bowlers%20will%20become%20that%20much%20more%20important%20because%20there%20was%20some%20reverse%20swing.%20Bumrah%20and%20Siraj's%20role%20will%20become%20more%20crucial%20and%20more%20importantly%20Jadeja%20will%20have%20to%20lead%20the%20spin%20attack.%20Jadeja%20will%20have%20to%20come%20to%20the%20party%20on%20his%20home%20ground%20in%20Rajkot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3