2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iea.org%2Freports%2Fthe-future-of-hydrogen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternational%20Energy%20Agency%20%3C%2Fa%3E(IEA)%2C%20the%20production%20of%20hydrogen%20is%20responsible%20for%20carbon%20dioxide%20emissions%20of%20around%20830%20million%20tonnes%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20per%20year.%20Interestingly%2C%20green%20hydrogen%20%E2%80%93%20produced%20by%20the%20electrolysis%20of%20water%20using%20renewable%20electricity%20%E2%80%93%20could%20save%20tonnes%20of%20this%20carbon%20dioxide%20emitted%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tap%20into%20green%20hydrogen%E2%80%99s%20potential%20and%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20a%20clean%2C%20secure%2C%20and%20affordable%20energy%20future%2C%20Haryana-based%20green%20hydrogen%20company%2C%20Hygenco%2C%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20construct%20and%20operate%20a%20100%20percent%20green%20hydrogen%20plant%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20would%20be%20the%20first%20operative%20green%20hydrogen%20production%20facility%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20will%20produce%20energy%20without%20emitting%20carbon%20dioxide%20into%20the%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Amit%20Bansal%2C%20CEO%20of%20Hygenco%20Green%20Energies%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20rapid%20pace%20of%20growth%20is%20already%20entailing%20a%20significant%20surge%20in%20the%20use%20of%20resources%2C%20especially%20fossil%20fuels.%20With%20over%2080%20percent%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F142537%2Findian-origin-scientist-team-fuel-from-sunlight%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20India%E2%80%99s%20fuel%20requirements%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebeing%20import-dependent%20and%20coal%20being%20the%20primary%20source%20of%20its%20electricit