0calling%20me%20a%20tomboy%20because%20I%20would%20wear%20loose%20clothes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWearing%20loose%20clothes%20was%20not%20a%20conscious%20fashion%20decision.%20I%20could%20never%20find%20clothes%20in%20my%20size%20and%20had%20to%20shop%20in%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%20section.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20people%20started%20calling%20me%20a%20tomboy.%20But%20this%20sort%20of%20bullying%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20restricted%20to%20school.%20I%20was%20even%20called%20out%20by%20my%20relatives.%20In%20fact%2C%20there%20was%20a%20time%20when%20I%20used%20to%20love%20swimming.%20But%20one%20day%20my%20swimming%20teacher%20told%20me%20that%20I%20should%20not%20wear%20a%20V-cut%20swimming%20costume%20because%20I%20looked%20%E2%80%98hideous%E2%80%99.%20And%20that%20feeling%20of%20humiliation%20stayed%20with%20me%20for%20so%20long%20that%20I%20started%20hating%20swimming%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Diksha%20many%20years%20to%20unlearn%20all%20of%20those%20things%20that%20were%20said%20about%20her%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20see%20the%20magic%20it%20%5Bunlearning%5D%20did%20to%20my%20health%20and%20mental%20health%20once%20I%20started%20letting%20go%20of%20the%20things%20that%20people%20said%20about%20me%20and%20the%20notions%20my%20immediate%20society%20had%20about%20body%20shape%20and%20appearances.%20What%20I%20have%20learnt%20in%20life%20is%20that%20if%20there%20are%20things%20that%20trouble%20you%20as%20a%20child%20and%20if%20you%20do%20something%20about%20them%20when%20you%E2%80%99re%20older%2C%20it%20gives%20you%20an%20innate%20sort%20of%20satisfaction.%20I%20never%20intended%20to%20become%20a%20body%20positivity%20influencer%20or%20creator%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20a%20lot%20of%20that%20unlearning%20began%20once%20Diksha%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20for%20college%20in%202013%20and%20started%20writing%20about%20her%20experiences%20in%20blog%20posts%20and%20then%20on%20Instag