%20ruled%20by%20the%20Royal%20Family%20of%20Sawant%20Bhonsles%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20The%20Sawant%20Bhonsle%20family%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20stay%20steeped%20in%20history%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20entering%20Sawantwadi%2C%20the%20air%20seems%20different.%20The%20villages%20are%20blanketed%20with%20a%20kind%20of%20mystique%2C%20and%20history%20will%20whisper%20to%20you%20from%20every%20corner%20if%20you%20take%20the%20time%20to%20listen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20as%20the%20land%20of%20the%20artists%2C%20the%20princely%20state%20was%20ruled%20by%20the%20Royal%20Family%20of%20Sawant%20Bhonsles.%20The%20Sawantwadi%20Palace%20was%20built%20by%20Khem%20Sawant%20III%20and%20its%20vibrant%20red%20laterite%20facade%20is%20complemented%20by%20arches%20that%20draw%20from%20English%20architectural%20styles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Sawant%20Bhonsle%20family%20decided%20to%20open%20their%20doors%20to%20the%20public%20as%20a%20homestay%2C%20it%20was%20backed%20by%20the%20intent%20to%20take%20Sawantwadi%20art%20one%20step%20ahead%20by%20making%20it%20accessible%20to%20people%20from%20all%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20boutique%20art%20hotel%20is%20built%20for%20you%20to%20experience%20these%20art%20forms%20in%20their%20purest%20form%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shraddha%20says.%20She%20and%20Lakham%20are%20the%2019th%20generation%20of%20the%20Sawant%20Bhonsle%20family.%20They%20are%20united%20by%20their%20shared%20passion%20for%20the%20arts%20and%20food%20(both%20are%20professional%20chefs%20who%20studied%20at%20the%20Culinary%20Institute%20of%20America).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20will%20see%2C%20the%20revival%20of%20the%20palace%20quarters%20and%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322666%2Fretired-couple-turns-ancestral-land-into-eco-friendly-konkan-homestay-sindhudurg-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejourney%20to%20a%20homestay%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20roots%20in%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20love%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20plan%20was%20to%20get%20married%20in%20Goa%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shraddha%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20while%20planning%2C%20we%20realised%20we%20had%20a%20beautiful%20palace%20right%20here.%20So%2C%20we%20began%20restoring%20it%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20saw%20potential.%20It%20was%20an%20informed%20decision%20by%20the%20family%20to%20turn%20a%20portion%20of%20it%20into%20a%20boutique%20hotel%20featuring%20six%20suite%20rooms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20said%20portion%20was%20called%20%E2%80%98Taisaheb%20Wada%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20wing%20dedicated%20to%20the%20five%20queens%20of%20Sawantwadi.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20palace%20continues%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337937%2Fbest-budget-homestay-in-uttarakhand-the-nanda-stone-mukteshwar-by-ashish-verma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20private%20residence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fthe-sawantwadi-palace-1-1707824253.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sawantwadi%20Palace%20was%20built%20by%20Khem%20Sawant%20III%20during%20his%20reign%20from%201755%20to%201803%20stands%20as%20the%20pride%20of%20the%20city%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fthe-sawantwadi-palace-1-1707824253.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fthe-sawantwadi-palace-1-1707824253-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fthe-sawantwadi-palace-1-1707824253-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads